body:
OK so recently, ever since the schedule of which game modes where coming to play in the following weeks was taken down, riot has REPEATED. THE. SAME. GAME MODES! 
two weeks will be ascension, then poroking, ascension, doom boots, (the thresh game mode.. don't remember the name), then ASCENSION. {{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 
and so on, what is the deal? where's arurf, one for all, hexakill (haven't seen hexakill in ages), nemisis draft, etc. Why are ascension and poroking on repeat? I get they took away the "summoners queue" for the "surprise" element, but it's just made the game modes worse, instead of a scheduled and balance of each game mode, we get "random" gamemodes. (aka, ascension and poroking) 
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
